MatchedRegions.transcript: Our tests employ three different types of vision transformers, vanilla VIT, date, and VIT with improved augmentations and regularization.

MatchedRegion.Text: We test on 3 different types of Vision Transformers- - Vanilla ViT, DeiT, and ViT with improved augmentations and regularization (ViT-AR).

MatchedRegions.transcript: We measure the increase in robustness to distribution sheets, i.e.
the increase in accuracy for datasets with shifted distributions.
We use adversarial, reward, and synthetic datasets.
